---
layout: base.njk
---
<section class="intro">
  <p>I'm Adil Nussipov. I write about technology, craft, and the way attention shapes how we live and work. These are long-form essays&mdash;things that took time to think through.</p>
</section>

<section>
  <p class="section-label">Recent Writing</p>
  <ul class="article-list">
    {% for post in collections.posts | head(5) %}
    <li class="h-entry">
      <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="u-url p-name">
        <span class="article-date dt-published">{{ post.date | postDate }}</span>
        <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
        {% if post.data.description %}
        <h4 class="p-summary">{{ post.data.description }}</h4>
        {% endif %}
      </a>
    </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
  <a href="/writing/" class="all-writing-link">All writing &rarr;</a>
</section>
